# game/day 11.rpy:177
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_6d970cc4:

    # "Although there are rainy days easing the heat, there's still so much different in temperature and I'm not in a good physical condition."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 21)
    "虽然有时下雨气温会下降,但温差太大,反而让我身体有点不舒服。"

# game/day 11.rpy:178
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_dcb981dd:

    # "I'm eating Hiyamugi for lunch with Grandpa and Grandma but I couldn't even feel like holding my chopsticks."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 24)
