# game/day 11.rpy:179
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_9f89d739:

    # fn "「I do like Hiyamugi, but I just don't have an\n appetite right now...{w} Probably it's because I'm\n having a heat stroke.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 27-29)
