# game/day 11.rpy:180
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_84ca9a64:

    # gm "「Is that okay?{w} Well then you can eat Grandma's\n speacial Umeboshi!{w} It works for summer heat.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 31-34)
    gm "哦，对了，[l]那就吃奶奶腌的梅干吧！{w} 这对夏天的暑气应该有帮助。"

# game/day 11.rpy:181
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_fee89ee2:

    # fn "「Wow.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: キャンプ02.ks (KS 5416)
    fn "「哇。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:182
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_fe733571:

    # "I reply as I receive a bottle filled with bright red pickled plums.{w} Then, I take a piece and put it in my mouth."
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/torahiko/11日目.ks (KS 36)
    "一边说着,一边递给我一瓶塞满了红彤彤的梅干的罐子。用筷子夹出一颗,并放进嘴里含着。"

# game/day 11.rpy:183
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_db1e4ec1:

    # fn "「...!! It's so sour!!{w} So salty!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 42)
    fn "……呜呜！！[l]好酸啊！！[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:184
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_64d1c9b2:

    # gm "「Well then, looks like it works.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 46)
    gm "是不是很有效果？"

# game/day 11.rpy:185
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_08c28440:

    # gp "「The taste is just right for me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 49)
    gp "对我来说刚刚好"

# game/day 11.rpy:186
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_fbb0424e:

    # "Grandpa says while also throw one into his mouth,{w} but his complexion doesn't change a bit.{w} Wow, the dull taste of the elderly is surely terrifying...!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 51)
    "爷爷也拿了一颗放入口中面不改色地嚼着。高龄人士的味觉迟钝真可怕……!"

# game/day 11.rpy:187
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_343bfa9f:

    # gm "「Oh, that's right.{w} [fn]-chan, if you don't have a\n plan today, could you deliver this Umeboshi to the\n village mayor's house?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 55-58)
    gm "啊，对了。[l]小博行，今天如果你没事的话，能不能帮我把这个梅干送去村长家？"

# game/day 11.rpy:188
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_2cb7edde:

    # gm "「Actually, this Umeboshi was taken from the plum tree\n at the village mayor's house.{w} I just had to pickle\n it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 61)
    gm "其实这个梅干啊，"

# game/day 11.rpy:189
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_ba5f544b:

    # fn "「Eh...{w} Sure, I understand.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 66)
    fn "诶……[l]嗯，知道了"

# game/day 11.rpy:190
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_f5bad268:

    # "I thought I'd sleep at home today because I'm feeling a bit sick in the summer,{w} but I guess I can't go against it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 68-69)
    "因为今天有点疲倦,本来想在家里睡觉的。但毕竟是寄居之身……也无法反驳。"

# game/day 11.rpy:195
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_747e3f45:

    # fn "「I'm going!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 75)
    fn "那[漏れ]出门了"

# game/day 11.rpy:196
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_1aabce83:

    # gm "「Here's the Umeboshi.{w} I'm glad that you are here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 78)
    gm "来，拿好。[l]这里面放了梅干。[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:197
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_1668c92a:

    # "The paper bag I was given contains a bottle."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 81)
