    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 963)
    fn "「嗯……?」"

# game/day 11.rpy:687
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_979f7a5d:

    # "While I was looking at the bookshelf lineup, I noticed something behind it."
