# game/day 11.rpy:694
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_8b378c75:

    # "But I can't clearly see what's the title on the cover, so I can't deny the possibility that it's just a manga magazine..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 972)
