# game/day 11.rpy:696
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_cb8a881b:

    # fn "「This is...{w} Is it okay to see it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 976)
    fn "「这个……[l]可以看吗?」"

# game/day 11.rpy:697
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_2a613fa1:

    # "No, there is no good reason.{w} This is a complete invasion of privacy.{w} But isn't Torahiko hiding it in such an easy-to-understand place a bad thing?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 978-979)
    "不,没有什么好理由。这是完全侵犯隐私。但虎彦把它藏在这么容易理解的地方,是不是一件坏事?"

# game/day 11.rpy:698
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_02e2a1f3:

    # "No, there must be a possibility that it's an ordinary manga magazine in the first place."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 981)
