# game/day 11.rpy:699
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_87b5dffe:

    # "No, in Minasato where there are few electronic devices..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 983)
    "不,在电子设备很少的水乡村……"

# game/day 11.rpy:700
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_462ecad7:

    # "Boys around this age will have no choice but to use paper media or delusions to comfort themselves."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 985)
