# game/day 11.rpy:701
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_ee71554d:

    # "No, if I pretend to have found it by accident while trying to take a manga on a bookshelf, Torahiko may forgive me..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 987)
