# game/day 11.rpy:702
translate chinese_simplified torahiko11_638c4666:

    # "No, what if it's an erotic book with insanely niche and hard content?{w} I won't be able to see Torahiko's face properly from now on!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 11日目.ks (KS 989-990)
