# game/day 11.rpy:1268
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_d38dcbc3:

    # "I need to take refuge somewhere cool.{p}Somewhere very, very cool."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 68)
    "我需要去一个凉快的地方避难。非常非常凉快的地方。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1269
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_6770c123:

    # "A pool.{p}I'd go jump in one right now,\nbut I can't really study in one."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 70)
    "游泳池。现在就可以跳进去,[l]但在那里没法学习。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1270
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_8334dc3c:

    # "The graveyard.{p}It'd probably send shivers down my spine...\nBut there aren't any desks there."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 72)
    "墓地。那里可能会让人毛骨悚然……但那里没有书桌。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1271
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_575770ab:

    # "Study on a grave?{p}If I did such a disrepectful thing,\nI'd be cursed all the way to my grandchildren."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 74)
    "在墓地学习?[l]如果做这种不敬的事情,会被诅咒到孙子那代的。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1272
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_bcb53d3a:

    # "No way."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: キャンプ02.ks (KS 1377)
    "不行。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1273
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_113282c8:

    # "The library!{p}It's a cool, quiet, air-conditioned place.{p}Plus, the only thing I can do there is study."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 78)
    "图书馆![l]那是凉爽、安静、有空调的地方。[l]而且,我在那里只能学习。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1274
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_0cdbb2b9:

    # "...I can't believe I didn't think of that first.{w=.2}\nThis heat must be really wearing me out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 80)
    "……我居然没想到这个。[l]这炎热真的把我逼坏了。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1275
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_3cb59369:

    # "I stuff all of my study materials into my bag.{p}...I guess it's time to go now?{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 82)
    "我把所有的学习资料塞进包里。[l]……好吧,该走了?"

# game/day 11.rpy:1277
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_9bc28045:

    # extend "I slowly stand up."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 84)
    extend "我慢慢地站起来。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1287
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_bff67deb:

    # "...So.{p}Here I am, at the library."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 86)
    "……所以。我现在在图书馆。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1288
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_cafbc113:

    # "The room is chilled by the\nwonders of modern society.{w=.2}\nIt welcomes me, as though I've been blessed."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 88)
    "这个房间被现代科技的奇迹——冷气冷却着。[l]它欢迎我,就像被祝福了一样。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1289
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_488b6957:

    # "Well, it was worth waiting 30 minutes for the bus.{p}Air conditioning, I love you!{p}I cheerfully make my way into the building."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 90)
    "好吧,等30分钟巴士是值得的。空调,我爱你!我高兴地走进楼里。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1290
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_f9e6d97e:

    # who "「I'm surprised to meet you in a place like this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 92)
    who "「在这种地方见到你真意外」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1294
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_fea50d10:

    # fn "{size=+15}「Gyaaah!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 94)
    fn "「哇呀啊啊!?」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1295
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_242c6b7f:

    # "A voice says my name from behind me,{w=.2}\nmaking me cry out in surprise.{p}I try to close my mouth, but I'm too slow."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 96)
    "一个声音从我身后叫我的名字,[l]让我惊讶地叫了出来。我想闭嘴,但太晚了。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1299
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_b362f40f:

    # "Oops."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 孝之助_m_09.ks (KS 61)
    "哎呀。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1300
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_d0e98b73:

    # "A-ahaha, everybody around me is staring.{p}That's what happens when you yell in a library..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 100)
    "啊哈哈哈,周围的人都在盯着我看。[l]这就是在图书馆大喊的后果……"

# game/day 11.rpy:1301
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_c49f98ce:

    # fn "「S-sorry...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 峻_m_04.ks (KS 309)
    fn "「对、对不起……」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1302
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_e15bfbab:

    # "I quietly apologize to everyone.{p}I turn around to face the person who startled me,{w=.2}\nand find Shin-kun there, looking shocked."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 104)
    "我安静地向大家道歉。我转过身去面对那个吓到我的人,[l]发现深君在那里,看起来很震惊。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1306
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_38b7533d:

    # "Do I look sad like this?{p}Or is him scaring me part of the cause."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 106)
    "我看起来那么悲伤吗?[l]或者他吓到我也是原因之一。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1307
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_556fccf5:

    # "...Ooh, his cold eyes cutting into me hurt.{p}What do you think I'd do, Shin-kun?!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 108)
    "……哦,他那冰冷的眼神刺痛了我。[l]你想让我怎么做,深君?!"

# game/day 11.rpy:1311
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_7ffa691d:

    # si "「You're supposed to be quiet in the library.{w=.2}\n Weren't you taught that in elementary school?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 110)
    si "「在图书馆要保持安静。[l]这点你小学没学过吗?」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1312
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_76a062a8:

    # fn "「Yes...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 380)
    fn "「是……」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1316
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_4556dbcd:

    # si "「Then try demonstrating your knowledge.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 161)
    si "「在图书馆要安静。[wdt]小学没教过吗？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1317
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_76a062a8_1:

    # fn "「Yes...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 380)
    fn "「是……」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1318
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_3a0d5f29:

    # "...Oh man, I'm getting really chewed out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 174)
    "……糟糕了。说不定会被吃掉啊我。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1319
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_e4b087cb:

    # "I'm like an ex-friend mince pie.{p}Or a bloody soup of small mushrooms."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 176)
    "前好友口味的迷你派。[l]加入小蘑菇的特製鲜红蕃茄汤。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1320
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_3530fdc5:

    # "More and more horrible dishes come to mind,\npassing in front of my eyes.{p}Help me, Gyoza fairy!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 179)
    "……稍微想像一下，我的眼前就不断出现了各式各样的恐怖料理。[l]呜呜，救命啊饺子妖精！"

# game/day 11.rpy:1324
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_f440a0ae:

    # si "「Well, that's how you usually are.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 186)
    si "「而且，你在平常就是，」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1325
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_ed4e2f30:

    # who "「What's wrong with maintaining the status quo?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 426)
    who "「……没有特别在做什么运动。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1326
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_ace0f203:

    # "A hand of salvation, not from a fairy,{w=.2}\nis extended to me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 191)
    "救我一命的，不是连有没有都不知道的妖精，[wdt]而是在这里的现实人物。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1327
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_e4ae21e0:

    # "The face of a familiar bear shows up.{p}It's Juuichi-san, here to put an end to\nShin-kun's drawn-out sermon."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 194)
    "突然出现的，是我熟稔的熊人。[l]把看来将会持续很久的，深的说教给制止的人，[wdt]是柔一。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1335
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_afbc06e5:

    # fn "「Oh, Juuichi-san.{w=.2} Good afternoon.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 206)
    fn "「啊，柔一。[wdt]午安。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1336
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_5dedc760:

    # "He raises his hand in response.{p}I-I've been saved.{p}Shin-kun is really merciless at times like these."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 208)
    "柔一举手握拳简短地打了声招呼。[l]得、[wdt]得救了。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1340
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_7702e399:

    # si "「...Well,{w=.2} whatever.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 215)
    si "「……啊，[wdt]是可以啦。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1341
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_d1a0f91f:

    # "He suddenly turns away.\nWe must have hit a sore spot."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 219)
    "深转过头去结束了话题。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1342
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_16b8cb94:

    # "Silence."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: キャンプ02.ks (KS 5702)
    "沉默。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1343
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_486859e8:

    # "More silence."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 224)
    "继续沉默。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1344
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_25c73160:

    # "Even more silence."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 226)
    "接着还是沉默。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1345
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_5918b564:

    # "...This is awkward. Too awkward.{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 228)
    "……这个糟糕。太糟糕了。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1347
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_ba89e531:

    # extend "I glance over at Juuichi-san, and he looks troubled\nwhile scratching his cheek."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 229)
    extend "看了看柔一，他也只是困扰地抓了抓脸颊表示。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1348
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_042d9a09:

    # "His expression tells me that we'd\nbest leave sleeping dogs lie.\nNo reinforcements. We're stranded."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 230)
    "一脸敬鬼神而远之，彷彿顿悟了什么的表情。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1349
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_0882a0f4:

    # "I need to get back on Shin-kun's good side.{p}It wouldn't be good for him to\nbe in a bad mood all summer."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 233)
    "可是，如果不做什么让深的心情恢复的话。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1350
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_f63cea62:

    # fn "「So, what book are you taking out?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 237)
    fn "「说起来，深是要来借什么书呢？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1355
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_29abf0b2:

    # si "「{cps=15}...{cps=40}This one.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 243)
    si "「[wds]……[rd]是这个。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1356
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_18369200:

    # "Although it took some time for the words to come,{w=.2}\nShin-kun bluntly hands his nook to me.{p}Mentally, I strike a triumphant pose."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 245)
    "虽然开口前有一小段时间的停顿，[wdt]不过深却很直接地把手上的书给我看。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1357
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_3bc9d474:

    # fn "「...What's this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 323)
    fn "「看你也不像是会看书的人啊？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1358
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_c47d4b30:

    # "My feeling of accomplishment is destroyed,{w=.2}\nthe instant I take a look at the book."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 252)
    "心中那些细微的兴奋感，[wdt]在看到递过来的书的瞬间就消失了。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1359
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_440098ba:

    # "It's an old-fashioned hardcover. That's fine.{p}The problem is that it's obviously written\nin a language that isn't English."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 341)
    "……所以说不要用那么冷淡的眼神看我嘛。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1365
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_5fb6d054:

    # "I flip through the pages,\nbut it's impossible for me to decipher."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 346)
    "「……咳嗯，是为了来写暑假作业的。[l]家里没有冷气，实在没办法集中精神。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1366
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_b8697a2e:

    # "Firstly, I don't get these slash and dot symbols.{p}I think these are European letters..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 353)
    "「我想也是那样。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1367
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_5c2ce0cd:

    # "...Oh, that reminds me.{p}Now that I think about it, I finally realize.{p}Shin-kun's mother is from France, isn't she?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 428)
    "虽然转移话题得很明显，[wdt]不过总之算是任务完成……了吧？"

# game/day 11.rpy:1368
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_ca52e31b:

    # fn "「What is this, Shin-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 435)
    fn "「哎，既然你都说了那试试看也无妨。[l]有推荐什么运动吗？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1369
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_0ecd803e:

    # si "「It's exactly what you think it is.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 439)
    si "「推、[wdt]推荐，吗……」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1370
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_b3c477fe:

    # fn "「French...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 443)
    fn "糟糕，什么都想不到。[l]该怎么说，没想到事情会发展成这样。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1374
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_17c1f112:

    # si "「Oui, c'est juste.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 282)
    si "「Oui, c'est juste」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1375
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_82af7001:

    # "His expression softens a little."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 286)
    "深原本那僵硬的表情，也稍微和缓了下来。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1376
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_86e21241:

    # "I think those were words of confirmation..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 288)
    "唔，这时候说的,[wdt]应该是肯定的意思吧……「就是这样」一类的？"

# game/day 11.rpy:1380
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_26312b08:

    # si "「This place has foreign language books too.{p} I read French regularly to keep my skills up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 293)
    si "「这里，也有放些未翻译的原文书。[l]为了不让母语变钝，[wdt]我会定期来看一些法文的书。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1381
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_9a884899:

    # si "「I'd like to have a conversation in French\n after reading it...{w} Amaki doesn't speak it, though.{p} I suppose that's a bit of a minor problem.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 298)
    si "「如果说，还有人会讲法语的话就太好了……[l]不过就连天木都不会说。[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1382
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_d090c9a3:

    # fn "「Oh, I see...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 303)
    fn "「咦，是这样啊……」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1383
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_7ac911dc:

    # "Unlike English, I rarely even experience French...{p}I guess you have to do that to stay at his level."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 305)
    "和英语不同，日常生活会用到法语的机会实在是非常少……"

# game/day 11.rpy:1384
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_4959c741:

    # "I used to think it was amazing\nhe could speak French,{p}but I guess it was the result of hard work."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 309)
    "会说法语好厉害！什么的，虽然以前曾经这么想过，[l]但这也是深私底下努力的结果吧。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1385
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_ede1f53b:

    # si "「Well, enough about me.{p} ...Why did you come to the library?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 314)
    si "……你又是为什么会来图书馆的？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1386
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_9f4e3f5a:

    # "He turns the question on me.{p}Wow, I got him into a better mood, didn't I?{p}It's rare that he uses one of my questions."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 316)
    "被深给反问了。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1390
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_8d7c3260:

    # si "「You're not much of a reader, are you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 323)
    si "「看你也不像是会看书的人啊？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1391
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_3e69151f:

    # "He sank my battleship.{p}A harsh blow from Shin-kun..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 325)
    "一发击沉。[l]果然，深的一击真的超严厉的……"

# game/day 11.rpy:1392
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_bcab1262:

    # fn "「I'm actually very delicate and pure!{p} It makes me cry when you say things like that!」 "
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 329)
    fn "「我，我也是很纤细很纯真的！[l]说那种话我可是会流血泪给你看的喔！」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1396
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_bef95801:

    # si "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 1046)
    si "「……」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1397
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_7b0e16f9:

    # "He glares at me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 339)
    "不屑的一瞥。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1398
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_771820b7:

    # "...Don't look at me with such cold eyes.{p}It was just a little joke, okay?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 341)
    "……所以说不要用那么冷淡的眼神看我嘛。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1399
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_6ed10eb3:

    # fn "「...Ahem, I'm working on my homework.{p} There's no air conditioning at home,\n so I couldn't concentrate.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 346)
    fn "「……咳嗯，是为了来写暑假作业的。[l]家里没有冷气，实在没办法集中精神。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1403
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_4e421173:

    # si "「That's what I thought.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 353)
    si "「我想也是那样。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1404
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_98704afc:

    # "If you already knew, then why did you ask..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 355)
    "事先想到了的话就不要问嘛……"

# game/day 11.rpy:1405
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_0803277d:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san, are you taking out a book too?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 358)
    fn "「柔一也是来借书的吗？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1406
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_f104b60c:

    # "I speak to Juuichi-san, who has been\nstanding there this whole time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 360)
    "我试着也向刚刚就一直沉默地在一旁看着的柔一搭话。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1411
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_409a5fcb:

    # ju "「Yes, that's right.{p} A new book in the 'Soft and Fair Goes Far'\n series has is out.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 366)
    ju "「啊，是啊。[l]是来看『以柔克刚』系列的新刊的。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1412
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_fd50d312:

    # "Wait, what?{p}Without thinking, I ask him to repeat himself."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 369)
    "是，你刚刚说什么？[l]我不假思索地就反问道。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1416
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_fd4f463c:

    # ju "「'Soft and Fair Goes Far'.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 375)
    ju "「所以说，是『以柔克刚』。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1417
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_5481202d:

    # fn "「Uhh, you can get porn at the library?」{w}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 378)
    fn "「那个，色情书刊是可以到图书馆借的吗？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1423
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_28b0d9fd:

    # "Juuichi-san strikes me with full force.{p}My field of vision goes black for a moment."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 385)
    "结果马上就被柔一打了。[l]完全没有留手的一击，我的视线瞬间黑了一下。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1424
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_4f1a2c50:

    # "Ow... I was just joking around.{p}It seems he didn't take it that way, though."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 388)
    "呜呜，明明是发挥机智想出来的搞笑的说。[l]对太认真的柔一看来没用吗……咕呜。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1425
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_d9c324da:

    # "Torahiko gets this every day,{w=.2}\nand he just takes it like it's nothing..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 391)
    "而且虎彦他每天都被这样暴打，[wdt]竟然还能一脸没事的样子……"

# game/day 11.rpy:1426
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_52a95b7d:

    # "It even seems like he enjoys\ntheir little back-and-forths.\nI wonder if this is what they call 'harmony'?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 394)
    "不……虎彦的情况，[wdt]可以视为他是"

# game/day 11.rpy:1427
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_c0ea6929:

    # "As I look over to Juuichi to talk about that,{w=.2}\n{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 398)
    "我一边想着这种事情一边看向柔一，"

# game/day 11.rpy:1429
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_d28f8848:

    # extend "he glares at me, and looks like he wants to say\nsomething.{w} I quickly change the subject."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 399)
    extend "他却是一脸想说什么的样子半眯着眼睛盯着我看。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1430
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_89459169:

    # fn "「A-ahem!{p} By the way, Shin-kun, do you play any sports?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 402)
    fn "「唔、[wdt]晤唉哼！[l]说起来，深你平常有在做什么运动吗？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1438
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_65f0e8ff:

    # si "「...Me?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 413)
    si "「……我？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1439
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_3152eb1c:

    # fn "「Yeah.{p} I think sports would be something you'd like.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 416)
    fn "「对对。[l]我觉得，深也很适合做运动的。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1440
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_2e13724e:

    # "Shin-kun looks confused."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 419)
    "深的表情一脸困惑。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1441
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_e0cc75dc:

    # "...Of course he would be.\nSorry for using you,\nI'll treat you to something nice some time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 420)
    "……这也是理所当然啦。抱歉只是为了转移话题才利用了你，现在想找什么更好的话题也很难啦。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1445
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_70059e25:

    # si "「...I'm not particularly into sports, though.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 426)
    si "「……没有特别在做什么运动。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1446
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_4cfd6102:

    # "I'm being awfully forward right now,{w=.2}\nbut I'm in the clear now... Right?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 53)
    "「热到完全没办法专心看书了啦……」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1451
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_25db0506:

    # si "「Well, that aside, I'd like to try one.{p} What would you recommend?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 435)
    si "「哎，既然你都说了那试试看也无妨。[l]有推荐什么运动吗？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1452
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_1062f65e:

    # fn "「R-recommend...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 439)
    fn "「推、[wdt]推荐，吗……」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1456
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_f2dade6f:

    # "Crap, I didn't think of that.{p}I didn't think things would go this way.{p}I'm sweating, despite the cool air."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 443)
    "糟糕，什么都想不到。[l]该怎么说，没想到事情会发展成这样。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1460
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_b975b0fb:

    # ju "「...No matter what you choose, you'll need strength.{p} Remember that, if you plan on\n playing with [ln].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 450)
    ju "「……没错，不管做什么体力都是很重要的。[l]就照西村的建议来试试也不错。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1461
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_55b201b3:

    # "A fatal blow from Juuichi-san..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 702)
    "「这个笨蛋。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1462
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_863b7f4e:

    # "I rummage around my bag,{w=.2}\nand pull out three cards.{p}I fan them out, and hold them up in front of me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 455)
    "我在内心的袋子里翻找着，[wdt]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1463
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_9e8f10cc:

    # "'Safe Answer'{p}'Appropriate Answer'{p}'Evade'"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 459)
    "「适当地回答。」[l]「敷衍地回答。」[l]「岔开话题。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1464
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_90479cc1:

    # "Those are my three options."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 463)
    "我可以做的选择，只有这三个。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1465
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_0eb7cd6c:

    # "Which one?{p}Which one do I choose?!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 465)
    "怎么办？[l]该怎么办才好啊，我！？"

# game/day 11.rpy:1482
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_31edb0fe:

    # "I steel myself, and select one.{p}The 'safe answer' card."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 492)
    "我下定决心选了其中一张卡片。[l]那是「适当地回答」的卡。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1486
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_c47af2ed:

    # fn "「Tennis would be a good match for you, wouldn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 498)
    fn "「网球的话应该挺适合的吧。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1487
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_3f0bd8ba:

    # si "「Tennis?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 501)
    si "「网球？」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1488
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_9272ff5c:

    # fn "「That's right.{w} It's not like soccer,\n where you're running around all the time,\n so I think it'd suit you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 504)
    fn "「对对。[l]不用像足球那样一直跑来跑去，我觉得应该还蛮适合深的喔。」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1489
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_2cf64ea5:

    # "...I can't believe what I'm saying.{p}It's like getting a burst of strength\nat the scene of a disaster."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 508)
    "……意外地我还挺会说话的嘛。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1490
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_478506d8:

    # "It remains to be seen whether or not\nI have the strength for this situation."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 514)
    "柔一在一旁困惑地看着。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1494
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_a8d1af6f:

    # ju "「I think tennis is a pretty intense sport, though-」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 515)
    ju "「不过网球算是相当激烈的运动，」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1495
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_4e0513b6:

    # "I quickly close Juuichi-san's mouth,\nbefore he says too much."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 517)
    "我连忙把说出多馀的话的柔一的嘴巴遮住。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1496
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_0f42e1eb:

    # "It seems he's still trying to speak,\nbut his voice is too muffled to be heard.{p}Okay, he's stopped."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 152)
    "啊不、我现在看起来好像很悲惨，[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1500
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_bef95801:

    # si "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 120)
    si "我一边擦着汗，一边兴高彩烈地在图书馆内走来走去。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1501
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_04315526:

    # "Shin-kun has his hand on his chin,\nand seems to be in deeo thought.{p}Hm, I'll need to give him another push."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 65)
    "「啊――不写了不写了！」"

# game/day 11.rpy:1502
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_4732e78b:

    # fn "「I think you'd look good in tennis wear, too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 234)
    fn "这整个暑假都要跟深冷战的话可真的不好受。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1503
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_d6b330c9:

    # "A pure white polo shirt, and large shorts.{p}Those would go great with his black fur."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 255)
    "那是看起来很旧的厚装书。这点还好。[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1507
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_a87bfe40:

    # si "「Sorry, but tennis is out of the question.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 140)
    si "这个，在图书馆吵闹会变这样也是理所当然啦……。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1508
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_59184beb:

    # "Furthermore, you could get a peek\nof his underwear up his shorts!{p}The demand for this must be through the roof!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 73)
    "当成前提这点才是不对的吧？"

# game/day 11.rpy:1512
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_ffa6e127:

    # "...Wait, did he just say it's out of the question?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 690)
    "深就已经直接走出图书馆了。[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1513
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_9ef1ff84:

    # fn "「O-out of the question...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 739)
    fn "结果只剩我一个人在图书馆里。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1514
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_4c404f97:

    # si "「I say that because I avoid\n long periods of exercise.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 928)
    si "图书馆内整个冻结了。[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1518
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 10日目.ks (KS 28)
    "……"

# game/day 11.rpy:1519
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_9845e9e0:

    # si "「I moved to Minasato for medical treatment.{p} I think I'm all right for the most part, though.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 299)
    si "就太好了……[l]不过就连天木都不会说。[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1520
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_38b62264:

    # si "「If I want to do something that requires strength,\n I need to think about it first.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 317)
    si "喔喔，看来深的心情终于变好了吗？[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1521
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_94c1d7b9:

    # "It was such a good idea, though...{p}I hung my head in defeat."
    ""

# game/day 11.rpy:1527
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_846f1bce:

    # ju "「How about you go talk to Takahara about it?{p} He should be finishing up with his club about now.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 75)
    ju "这样的话，不找个凉爽的地方去避暑是不行了。[l]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1528
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_5e927f21:

    # si "「All right then, I'll give it a try.{p} ...Now, if you'll excuse me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 79)
    si "虽然很想马上跳进去，但不能读书所以不行。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1529
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_12251b08:

    # ju "「Later.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS L495)
    ju "以后再说。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1534
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_abe69d54:

    # "The automatic door slides open,\nand Shin-kun steps outside."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 421)
    "抱歉只是为了转移话题才利用了你，现在想找什么更好的话题也很难啦。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1535
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_839ca0ca:

    # "Since the light out there blinds me,\nI can't see him leave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 466)
    "该怎么办才好啊，[l]我！？"

# game/day 11.rpy:1539
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_df3931d9:

    # ju "「Hey, [ln].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS L497)
    ju "嘿，[ln]。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1540
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_14a10b68:

    # "While I'm feeling discouraged,\nJuuichi-san speaks to me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 521)
    "很好，姆嘎姆嘎语转换完成。"

# game/day 11.rpy:1541
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_ab554575:

    # fn "「...What?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 61)
    fn "这样就证明完了……[wdt]什么的，[wdt]"

# game/day 11.rpy:1545
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_5f940f17:

    # ju "「Do you want to go somewhere to relax?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS L499)
    ju "你想去哪里放松一下？"

# game/day 11.rpy:1546
translate chinese_simplified juuichi11_tennis_b41c2d23:

    # "His kindness pierces me.{p}Without thinking, I hug Juuichi-san."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_01.ks (KS 530)
